ActIndian Act
SubjectProgram and service expenditures O-Pipon-Na-Piwi Cree Nation
PrecisOrder extending the authority of the Minister of Indigenous and Northern Affairs, and the Minister of Health, to continue providing programs and services, normally available to Bands on reserve, to O-PIPON-NA-PIWIN CREE NATION until the lands at South Indian Lake are set apart as reserve or until March 31, 2023.
